    "## Specify the linkage indicator"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3968a4b8-9114-486c-837e-4bd0c8513d9e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "COSIE requires a indicator dictionary to specify the cross-section linkage used during training."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "2e393efe-981b-40c0-a418-c76d7eab0cf9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "Linkage_indicator = {\n",
    "        ('s1', 's2'): [('RNA', 'RNA')]\n",
    "    }"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,

    "## Define COSIE Model and Perform Integration"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a94b9b52-b30f-4831-bdc7-2f3939105aa4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "After training, embeddings will be saved to `file_path` in `.npy` format."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "d8a9cc4d-aad4-44b9-915b-2e12187a767f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "All modalities: ['RNA', 'HE', 'Protein']\n",
      "-------- Encoder description --------\n",
      "Encoder [RNA]: Input 50 → Hidden [256, 128]\n",
      "Encoder [HE]: Input 50 → Hidden [256, 128]\n",
      "Encoder [Protein]: Input 20 → Hidden [256, 128]\n",
      "-------- Dual prediction module description --------\n",
      "Predictor [RNA → HE]: [128, 512, 512, 128]\n",
      "Predictor [HE → RNA]: [128, 512, 512, 128]\n",
      "Predictor [RNA → Protein]: [128, 512, 512, 128]\n",
      "Predictor [Protein → RNA]: [128, 512, 512, 128]\n",
      "Using device: cuda:0\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "model = COSIE_model(config, feature_dict)\n",
    "optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=config['training']['lr'])\n",
    "device = torch.device('cuda:0' if torch.cuda.is_available() else 'cpu')\n",
    "print(f'Using device: {device}')"
   ]
  },
